title: Alice In Chains Unplugged
description:
Alice In Chains - MTV Unplugged DVD RIP
The Seattle grunge rockers go acoustic in a thirteen-song set from "MTV Unplugged." Features non-broadcast bonus tracks ("Angry Chair"; "The Killer is Me") in addition to "Heaven Beside You," "Down in a Hole," and more of their hits.
